description.description_en:
Want a trinket for your sweater? This owl pendant necklace would be your best choice. The pendant has exquisite hollow, romantic heart shape and  inlayed crystal that show wearer's elegance. Wearing it, you will become the focus of attention.A good match for sweater, showing your special taste.
Retro owl pattern has good moral, symbolizing wise and good luck.
Exquisite hollow, heart shape and shinning crystal, full of womanliness.
Long chain is easy to arrange.
